snippet.title: Monopoly IO - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Play Monopoly IO here - http://benbean.openode.io/monopoly-io/
Check out the subreddit here - https://www.reddit.com/r/MonopolyIO/

Monopoly IO brings the classic board game to the web. Play in either public or private matches, roll the dice, buy properties, and bankrupt your opponents! Gamers can now enjoy Monopoly from any device supporting WebGL, and play with anyone from around the world.
